wp enqueue media "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
================================================================

NAME
----

wp enqueue media - `wp_enqueue_media` is the function to load the WP 3.5 Media uploader

SYNOPSIS
--------

`wp_enqueue_media` is the function to load the WP 3.5 Media uploader
scripts and environment.

USAGE
-----

Strongly suggest to use this function on the `admin_enqueue_scripts`
action hook. Using it on `admin_init` hook breaks it.

